Package gobblin.config.store.hdfs

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SimpleHDFSConfigStore
    An implementation of ConfigStore backed by HDFS.
    SimpleHDFSConfigStoreFactory
    An implementation of ConfigStoreFactory for creating SimpleHDFSConfigStores.
    SimpleHDFSStoreMetadata
    A metadata accessor for an HDFS based ConfigStore.
    SimpleLocalHDFSConfigStoreFactory
    Extension of SimpleHDFSConfigStoreFactory that creates a SimpleHDFSConfigStore which works for the local file system.
